at Moses.

22:58.986 --> 23:00.204
What do you want?

23:00.248 --> 23:00.857
That's when you saw
the wire,

23:00.901 --> 23:01.815
What do you want?

23:01.858 --> 23:03.425
took it,
didn't tell Brannigan

23:03.469 --> 23:05.775
or anyone else
in your department,

23:05.819 --> 23:08.082
and you've been wrestling
with your conscience ever since.

23:08.125 --> 23:11.259
And right now, your conscience
has gotten the upper hand --

23:11.302 --> 23:16.569
which is why you left the tape
on my doorstep last night.

23:16.612 --> 23:19.572
See, I think we got this
the wrong way 'round.

23:19.615 --> 23:23.053
I should be asking you
what you want.

23:23.097 --> 23:25.665
It wasn't me.

23:25.708 --> 23:27.623
I didn't leave anything
at your house.

23:27.667 --> 23:33.368
