23:38.591 --> 23:39.287
♪♪

23:39.330 --> 23:42.638
Even your partner knew.

23:42.682 --> 23:44.248
What do you want me to do?

23:44.292 --> 23:45.075
First thing tomorrow morning,
go back up on the stand,

23:45.119 --> 23:48.862
What do you want me to do?

23:48.905 --> 23:51.647
and tell the jury
you lied about your gun.

23:51.691 --> 23:53.257
[Sighs]

23:53.301 --> 23:53.693
Michael Rossi was prepared
to follow his conscience.

23:53.736 --> 23:57.697
[Sighs]

23:57.740 --> 23:59.481
