24:41.305 --> 24:44.483
Hello, Mr. Dante.

24:44.526 --> 24:45.919
So...?

24:45.962 --> 24:49.879
So you discover a snitch
in your organization,

24:49.923 --> 24:52.360
and they die.

24:52.403 --> 24:55.189
Has to be.

24:55.232 --> 25:00.237
