25:07.331 --> 25:09.769
So?Martha: I think that's old.

25:09.812 --> 25:12.032
I think that's an old way
of doing things.

25:12.075 --> 25:14.469
Hm.
Yeah.

25:14.513 --> 25:16.297
And you strike me
as a modern man.

25:16.340 --> 25:17.907
Ah.

25:17.951 --> 25:19.256
A leader who leads

25:19.300 --> 25:22.085
with the cool side
of his brain

25:22.129 --> 25:25.175
and not the hot.

25:25.219 --> 25:26.220
What you want?

25:26.263 --> 25:28.831
A life.

25:28.875 --> 25:31.442
I want to save a life.

25:31.486 --> 25:33.880
Who is he?
She.

25:33.923 --> 25:35.577
It's a she.

25:44.281 --> 25:46.980
I think you can win
this election.

